ugh the Amazon Handmade platform with the right products, promotions, and customer service.</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <h3>#7. Sell designs via Merch by Amazon</h3> <p>Selling designs via <a href="https://merch.amazon.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-schema-attribute="">Merch by Amazon</a> is a popular way for designers to make money on Amazon. Merch by Amazon is a print-on-demand platform that allows designers to upload their designs, such as t-shirts, hoodies, and other apparel. Then sell them on Amazon.</p> <p>The best part? There are no upfront costs or inventory requirements! All you have to do is: create an account, upload your designs, and let Amazon handle the rest.</p> <p>Once a customer purchases your products, Amazon handles production, shipping, and customer service. All while giving you a healthy percentage of each sale. Itâ€™s a hassle-free way for creative minds who want to make money on amazon without spending much startup capital.</p> <figure id="attachment_2544" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="size-full wp-image-2544 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Merch-by-Amazon-is-an-extremely-easy-way-to-earn-without-spending-money-1.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="630" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Merch-by-Amazon-is-an-extremely-easy-way-to-earn-without-spending-money-1.jpg 1200w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Merch-by-Amazon-is-an-extremely-easy-way-to-earn-without-spending-money-1-300x158.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Merch-by-Amazon-is-an-extremely-easy-way-to-earn-without-spending-money-1-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Merch-by-Amazon-is-an-extremely-easy-way-to-earn-without-spending-money-1-768x403.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Merch-by-Amazon-is-an-extremely-easy-way-to-earn-without-spending-money-1-400x210.j