 can help designers reach a wider audience for their designs.</li> </ul> </td> <td class="acssd67e4"> <ul> <li><strong>Competition:</strong> There is a lot of competition on Merch by Amazon, so it can be difficult for designers to stand out.</li> <li><strong>Approval process:</strong> Merch by Amazon has an approval process, making it difficult for some designers to qualify.</li> <li><strong>Pricing:</strong> The prices set by Merch by Amazon for printing and shipping can impact the productâ€™s final price, affecting sales.</li> </ul> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <table class="table table-hover acss73184"> <tbody> <tr> <td class="acss9b509">ðŸ’¡ Selling designs via Merch by Amazon can be a great way for designers to make money on Amazon. While there is competition and an approval process, with the right designs, optimization of product listings, and promotion, designers can earn passive income through the Merch by Amazon platform.</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <h3>#8. Flip online retail store products using online arbitrage</h3> <p>Online arbitrage involves finding products at a lower price on one platform, then reselling them at a higher price on Amazon or other eCommerce platforms. This can be done with almost any product category and requires minimal investment.</p> <p>For this way of money-making, you can open an Amazon store to sell your products.</p> <p>To start, you need to find a reliable source of products with super competitive prices.</p> <p>One option is to look for clearance items in other online retail stores or search for overstocked or discontinued products sold at a discount. Or you can consider buying from Chinese sites, like Taobao or 1688.</p> <p>Once you have found a product you want to sell, itâ€™s important to research its sales history and demand before investing in inventory. Also, you should determine your product price by checking the prices of other online competitors on the platform youâ€™re selling in.</p> <p>Now itâ€™s time to list your products for sale on Amazon and/or Shopify to start getting that money.</p> <figure id="attachment_2548" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="size-full wp-image-2548 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1.jpg 1280w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1-400x225.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1-800x450.jpg 800w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="size-full wp-image-2548 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1.jpg 1280w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1-400x225.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-can-earn-money-by-online-arbitrage-too-1-800x450.jpg 800w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img><figcaption c